  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to analyse the anatomic influence of the ribs related to the
      incidence and severity of burst spine fractures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To analyse the anatomic influence of the ribs related to the incidence and severity of burst
      spine fractures, with the measurements of kyphosis, vertebral collapse and vertebral canal
      narrowing
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
